title: Mariah Carey-Heartbreaker [OFFICIAL IPOD MUSIC VIDEO]
description:
Mariah Carey-Heartbreaker [OFFICIAL IPOD MUSIC VIDEO]

Extension: .MP4

Quality (For Ipod): HQ


Video Release Year: 1996



       Heartbreaker is one of Mariah's hit number one singles featuring a rap artist. In the song Jay Z can be heard but is not shown in the video. 

The video starts off with Mariah's friends dragging her over to a theater where they believe Mariah's boyfriend is cheating on her. Mariah shows that she does not want to be there but is shocked to see her boyfriend sitting with another girl dressed in red. An upset Mariah follows the other girl to the bathroom to ask questions after the girl is pelted with popcorn by Mariah's friends. And angry girlfriend turns around to Mariah once they are both in the restroom and starts a fight.

After Mariah accidentally opens a occupied stall, the girlfriend leaves. The video then turns into a series to movies played out in the theater featuring Mariah, including an animated one during Jay Z's rapping part. 

Finally Mariah comes back into the theater carrying a large soda which she dumps over her ex-boyfriend before leaving.
